Package com.github.tadukoo.view.lookandfeel

Class TadukooTheme

java.lang.Object
com.github.tadukoo.view.lookandfeel.TadukooTheme
public class TadukooTheme extends Object
Theme class for TadukooLookAndFeel. You can use the builder via the builder() method to construct it and specify whatever customizations you want.
Since:
Alpha v.0.2
Version:
Alpha v.0.3
Author:
Logan Ferree (Tadukoo)
